### Document ID Generation

```
Formula:
  doc_id = "DG-" + SHA256(file_hash + ":" + filename + ":" + secret_key)[:32].upper()

Example:
  file_hash = "a3f9c2e1..."
  filename  = "contract.pdf"
  secret    = "my-secret"
  
  combined  = "a3f9c2e1...:contract.pdf:my-secret"
  doc_id    = "DG-96C568B3A93AC4093DCCAB2EFBEA17C"

Properties:
  ✅ Reproducible  — same file always generates same DocID
  ✅ Tied to content — filename change → different DocID
  ✅ Secret-bound  — only this system can generate valid DocIDs
  ✅ Human-readable — DG- prefix makes it recognizable
```

