## 🛡️ Security Techniques

| Technique | Implementation | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Timing-safe comparison** | `hmac.compare_digest()` | Prevents timing-based attacks on hash comparison |
| **Keyed MAC** | HMAC-SHA256 with secret | Prevents hash forgery |
| **Secrets in environment** | `.env` + python-dotenv | Keeps bot token out of source code |
| **No file storage** | Only hashes stored | User documents never touch our disk |
| **Git-ignored secrets** | `.gitignore` blocks `.env` | Prevents accidental credential leak |
| **Secret binding** | DocID includes secret | DocIDs cannot be forged externally |

