| Operation | Time Complexity | Space Complexity |
|---|---|---|
| SHA-256 hash | O(n) where n = file size | O(1) output |
| HMAC-SHA256 | O(n) | O(1) output |
| SHA3-256 | O(n) | O(1) output |
| Merkle tree build | O(n log n) | O(n) |
| Merkle root verify | O(log n) | O(log n) |
| Registry lookup by hash | O(d) where d = total docs | O(1) per user |

